@startuml artefatos-saida
title Artefatos de saída em output/\nGerados após construção dos grafos (giscus/giscus)

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam componentStyle rectangle

package "Aplicação" as app {

  component [ConsoleMenu\nopção 6] as menuExport
  component [ConsoleMenu\nopção 7] as menuReport
  component [DesktopController] as desktop

  component [GraphExportApplicationService] as exportSvc
  component [OutputReportService] as reportSvc
  component [GraphSummaryService] as summarySvc
  component [GraphAnalysisService] as analysisSvc
  component [ComparativeGraphAnalysisService] as compareSvc
}

folder "output/" as output #F5F5F5 {

  together {
    component [comments-graph.gexf] as f1
    component [issue-closure-graph.gexf] as f2
    component [pull-request-graph.gexf] as f3
    component [integrated-graph.gexf] as f4
    component [integrated-graph-gephi.gexf] as f5 <<recomendado>>
  }

  together {
    component [graph-summary.txt] as t1
    component [integrated-analysis.txt] as t2
    component [comparative-analysis.txt] as t3
  }
}

component [Gephi] as gephi
actor Usuário

menuExport --> exportSvc
desktop --> exportSvc
exportSvc --> f1 : GexfExporter\n(labels vN)
exportSvc --> f2
exportSvc --> f3
exportSvc --> f4 : GexfExporter
exportSvc --> f5 : GephiPresentationExporter\n(logins + layout + viz)

menuReport --> reportSvc
desktop --> reportSvc
reportSvc --> summarySvc
reportSvc --> analysisSvc
reportSvc --> compareSvc

summarySvc --> t1 : resumo dos 4 grafos,\ntop arestas, graus amostra
analysisSvc --> t2 : 11 blocos de métricas\ndo grafo integrado
compareSvc --> t3 : densidade e arestas\ncomparando os 4 grafos

f5 --> gephi : importação visual
t1 --> Usuário
t2 --> Usuário
t3 --> Usuário

note right of f5
  **Recomendado para apresentação**
  • nós com login real
  • posição radial por grau
  • peso real + visualWeight
end note

note bottom of t2
  Conteúdo típico:
  grau, densidade, PageRank,
  eigenvector, closeness, betweenness,
  clustering, assortatividade,
  comunidades, bridging ties,
  aberturas de PR por usuário
end note

note bottom of output
  Diretório padrão: output/
  (user.dir/output ou override em testes)
end note

@enduml
